column1: # coordinate_x : longitude bearing using coordinate system using Borneo RSO / Timbalai 1948
# coordinate_y : latitude bearing using coordinate system using Borneo RSO / Timbalai 1948
# elevation_m: altitude of the site from sea level in metre
# forest cover: percentage of forest cover occupying a 1 sq. km area, where the site lies
# canopy height: top tree canopy height in metre
# water occurence: percentage of water bodies present in a 1 sq. km area, where the site lies
# distance to road: euclidean distance from the site to the known road networks
# human population count: estimated number humans residing at the site
